{"tid":684522,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)奪面雙雄 最後一強 天眼救未來","createTime":"2018-05-30T15:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T19:07:08.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c465e1419517f83005ae86bfac0827cbfa93021c","tid":684522,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:14:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=nXJoC05fDDEosIck8i9fsozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=b5d5bb57\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=nXJoC05fDDEosIck8i9fsozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=23eaf6ce\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=nXJoC05fDDEosIck8i9fsozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=4ed1ed53\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/49/Face_off_movie.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F49%2FFace_off_movie.jpg&h=9f648169&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://image.tpwang.net/image/%E6%95%91/movie-%E6%95%91%E4%B8%96%E4%B8%BB/%E6%95%91%E4%B8%96%E4%B8%BB49472.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.tpwang.net%2Fimage%2F%25E6%2595%2591%2Fmovie-%25E6%2595%2591%25E4%25B8%2596%25E4%25B8%25BB%2F%25E6%2595%2591%25E4%25B8%2596%25E4%25B8%25BB49472.jpg&h=766b0fb2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/d2i5Jusk6oFpNR34Syp281wnpsm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.tmdb.org%2Ft%2Fp%2Foriginal%2Fd2i5Jusk6oFpNR34Syp281wnpsm.jpg&h=04c1c6cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.肖恩&middot;阿切爾（約翰&middot;屈伏塔）是聯邦調查局的高級探員，20多年的警探生涯辦過無數大案子，可是他終其一生都在追捕奸詐狡猾的恐怖份子卡斯特&middot;特洛伊（尼可拉斯&middot;凱吉） ，無惡不作的卡斯特也正是殺害阿切爾獨生子的凶手，讓阿切爾發誓要親自抓他到案入網。<br />\n終於在多次線人的密告之下，阿切爾終於有機會親自逮捕他歸案，趕在卡斯特與他弟弟波利克斯搭機逃亡之前，將他們繩之以法，在一陣槍戰之後，以損傷七名探員為代價......<br />\n<br />\n2.有一個這樣的理論：宇宙中存在多個平行世界，而且每個平行世界裡都有一個你存在，而且所有平行世界裡面的自己會分攤整個宇宙中你所具備的能量。所以，只要平行世界中的你都消失了，那所有的能量將匯聚到最後的一個人身上。正是為了這個目的，奪取所有人的能量，在遙遠的未來，名叫基比（李連杰飾）的殺手穿越時空殺掉了123個平行世界中的自己，獲得了超能力。而這時，世界中只剩下自己和另外一個平行世界...<br />\n<br />\n3.克里斯&middot;強森擁有可以看見未來，並以行動改變未來的能力，不過擁有特殊能力的他，受不了政府和醫學機構的檢查，於是隱藏起來混在拉斯維加斯的小賭場賭博和變魔術維生。<br />\n不過此時有FBI幹員寇莉&middot;佛瑞斯前來找尋克里斯&middot;強森，原來為了要避免恐怖組織炸掉洛杉磯核能電廠的陰謀，佛瑞斯必須盡速找到強森並且改變這件可怕的未來..<br />\n<br />\n11 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=nXJoC05fDDEosIck8i9fsozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=5004f65b\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=nXJoC05fDDEosIck8i9fsozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e63d8ce6\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36be578a026112f4ef83abdb76d739622ee5e990","tid":684522,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:15:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b338eefef9661a8c2624c29769807d97fc9c9e","tid":684522,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:30:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b6b791279db949e02f1b090d5a6de0adcc191b","tid":684522,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:00:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1cff2a024f71b6827b7d62cd06940cc63e86d9c","tid":684522,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:02:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a38ccfa666d511255877b6678c2919e11951cc53","tid":684522,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:51:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf850d33b680ba840737793d8b16bfbf3108575","tid":684522,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T19:07:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}